## LAMP stack stands for - Linux for OS, Apache for webserver, MySQL for RDBMS, PHP for scripting
## Alternatives can be
## Linux, Unix OS             -- L (OS) ;# Windows (WAMP stack)
## Apache, Nginx, Lighttpd    -- A (WebServer)
## MySQL, MariaDB, PostgreSQL -- M (Database)
## PHP, Python, Perl          -- P (Scripting)

I will be using Ansible playbooks to run this setup.
